				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\Omega_{src} \propto \delta^2$\end{document}. Sensitivity gains can furthermore be achieved with a large field of view of the instrument, observing multiple sources at a time and effectively multiplying the attainable observation time T.
