				\begin{document}$1/\Theta_{p}^{2}$\end{document}, smaller pixels sizes are strongly disfavoured. The improvement of angular resolution at smaller pixel size is also found to be modest in our studies (see also [95]). Alternative analyses may lead to significant benefits from smaller pixel sizes, but this has not yet been demonstrated.
